BRAND NEW, AFFORDABLE, FUSS- FREE & IMMEDIATE MOVE-IN UNITS AVAILABLE FOR STAY, TO WORK FROM HOME ( WFH ) OR PLAINLY AS WORK SPACE !!

MODERN, FULLY-FURNISHED LIFESTYLE SERVICED APARTMENTS EQUIPED WITH FREE WIFI, WORK DESKS & CHAIRS SUITABLE FOR WORKING FROM HOME OR ALSO TO STAY !

RESIDENSI HARMONI ONE
is a hassle-free concept serviced apartment in the Mont Kiara Enclave. Modern convenience at your door-step !

 We have total units of only 53 cosy & comfortable fully -furnished choices of 1, 2 or 3 rooms ranging from 400 - 900 sqft units.

 Only 3 years old and strategically located within Mont Kiara, Desa Sri Hartamas, Publika and Solaris residential area for the International community and expat families.

 Shopping malls nearby includes 5 malls - 1MK, Publika, Solaris,Hartamas Shopping Centre and the latest Kiara 163.

 Closeby are banks and 3 International Schools - Garden International School, Mont Kiara International School, and French School of KL and The Kiara Medical Centre.

 Many choices of restaurants and bars in the vicinity for a night out of fun & leisure.

 This location is also very accessible as it is built right next to the North - South Expressway (PLUS), which connects to the Duta - Ulu Kelang

 Highway, Penchala Link and the Sungai Buloh Highway. Other highways that are easily accessible are SPRINT Highway and Lebuhraya Damansara - Puchong (LDP).

 Extra Plus : Reasonable rental rates for this convenient & great location !

Ciri-ciri Utama:

★ Tanah yang Luas : 5000 Sqft
★ Luas Binaan Rumah 3000 Sqft
★ Bilik Tidur: 3 blk fully funished bersama Aircond system setiap ruang
★ Bilik Mandi: 2 bersama waterheater
★ Ruang Tamu yang Luas dan Selesa bersama meja makan 8 seater yang mewah dengan Aircond system dual inverter terbaru
★ Ruang Keluarga yang Berasingan
★ Dapur Moden dan Serba Lengkap dengan Kabinet Berkualiti Tinggi

★ Fully Furnished: Semua perabot dan dekorasi berkualiti tinggi disertakan! Tinggal bawa diri sahaja! iaitu Set sofa, meja makan, katil, almari, peralatan dapur, dll. Jika nk rumah kosong pn boleh diuruskan
★ Aircond, Lampu dan Kipas di Setiap Ruangan
★ Ciri-ciri tambahan: Laman rumah yang luas, garaj untuk beberapa kereta, pagar keliling yang tinggi dan bersih, CCTV, Lampu switch wifi controller dll.
🌳 Kelebihan Tanah: Telah dipasang weedmat bagi memastikan tiada rumput yang tumbuh semula. Bahagian laman belah belakang terdapat ruang tanah yang kecil untuk tanaman seperti ulam, daun pandan, serai dll.

Tanah yang luas memberikan ruang untuk aktiviti luar keluarga, berkebun, atau bahkan membina fasilitas tambahan seperti kolam renang atau taman permainan anak-anak.
Privasi dan ketenangan yang diidamkan.
🚗 Kemudahan Berdekatan: KTM serendah, ECRL yang bakal siap sekitar 2027(estimate), 30 mins to genting highland, 15 mins to Perodua Cooperate Rawang, 40mins to KL, 15mins to KPJ Rawang dll

Terdapat Sekolah Rendah Kebangsaan, Sekolah Menengah, Sekolah Kebangsaaan Cina, Little Caliph dll

Terima kasih!

name: ANDY ONO
body:
Description:
Situated along Jalan Stapok Utama there are retail shops on the lower floors which are great to serve the residents’ immediate convenience and necessities. the homes are able to accommodate singles and also families, as the smallest unit has 1 bedroom and 1 bathroom, whilst the biggest units has 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms. Additionally, the residents are able to use facilities such as the indoor gym, BBQ area, swimming pool, steam room, and enjoy the peaceful landscaped garden. HK Square is adjacent to residential areas that include Royal Garden, Taman Seri Emas , Rancangan Perumahan Batu Kawa, Everbright Estate, and Batu Kawa amongst others. Other than that, there are a few condominium and apartment projects close by, and commercial and retail shops that are quite convenient as well. Schools nearby include Sunny Hill School, SJK Chung Hua No. 6, Sekolah Kebangsaan Garland, and amenities such as the Sarawak General Hospital, Balai Polis Sg. Maong , and several shopping malls are not too far away.
